Side displays two files next to each other for comparison. For example:

[mikal@localhost side]$ ./side "cat - < %s" long short
Warning, do not use this command in a secure environment...
  cat - < long > /tmp/side.Agou7k                                       |cat - < short > /tmp/side.uQTNBm
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------
   1                                                                    | 1                                                                  
   2                                                                    | 2                                                                  
   3                                                                    | 3                                                                  
++ 4                                                                    |*                                                                   
++ 5                                                                    |*                                                                   
++ 6                                                                    |*                                                                   
++ 7                                                                    |*                                                                   
++ 8                                                                    |*                                                                   
++ 9                                                                    |*                                                                   
++ 10                                                                   |*                                                                   
[mikal@localhost side]$ 

